<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$yin-de-yi-72" href="/people/yin-de-yi-72">殷德义</a>，<strong title="制片人、导演、编剧" class="zu-question-my-bio">制片人、导演、编剧</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="5">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ti-yu-shi-jie-de-cai-niao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ti-yu-shi-jie-de-cai-niao" class="zg-link" title="体育世界的菜鸟">体育世界的菜鸟</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cong-yun-70" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cong-yun-70" class="zg-link" title="丛云">丛云</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-mi-75-21" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-mi-75-21" class="zg-link" title="张米">张米</a></span>
