</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1018951" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">1、提炼故事核；<br>2、围绕故事核，展开想象；<br>3、搭建框架大纲；<br>4、开始写吧！


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
